维护速查

[Description]
<!-- Section-ID: S13_MAINTAINER_REFERENCE -->
| Name | Kind | Location | Purpose | Notes |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| `main` | Function | fixture concept | 串联主流程 | 调用读取、建模和渲染 |
| `buildModel` | Function | fixture concept | 构建模型 | 不应修改输入配置 |

[UML]
None

[Detail]
维护速查必须是 Markdown 表格。
